tes for these stochastic\nfirst order methods. Finally, the stochastic gradient mapping and the Moreau\nsmoothing mapping introduced in the present paper lead to simple and intuitive\nproofs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2020 17:48:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Mar 2020 13:50:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-10"}
