ottom surface) quantum Hall state. Simulations using the simplest\npossible theoretical approach are in line with the basic experimental findings,\ndescribing correctly the central features of the transitions from classical to\nquantum transport in the respective areas of our multicomponent charge carrier\nsystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2020 19:02:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-02"}
