SA. We also report several unique neutrino\nsignatures, which are significantly dependent on both the time and the viewing\nangle, if observed, possibly providing a rich information regarding the onset\nof the MR-driven explosion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Mar 2020 11:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 13:59:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
