atter. A possible explanation of these\nresults is the dynamical response of the gas regulator system of Lilly et al.\n2013 to a uniform time-varying inflow, as previously proposed in Wang et al.\n2019.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Mar 2020 15:54:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
